DESCRIPTION {
    How big are the clans, that means: how many people do have the same name? 
    Please list the name and the clan size (biggest clan first).
}

ANSWER {
    SELECT name, count(*)
    FROM person
    GROUP BY name
    ORDER BY count(*) DESC;
}

